PER1A_ARMRU - Also known as HPRC1. Experimental evidence at protein level: Swiss-Prot protein existence level 1. Removal of H(2)O(2), oxidation of toxic reductants, biosynthesis and degradation of lignin, suberization, auxin catabolism, response to environmental stresses such as wounding, pathogen attack and oxidative stress. These functions might be dependent on each isozyme/isoform in each plant tissue. From Armoracia rusticana (Horseradish) (Armoracia laphatifolia).
